Package: Dominance
Title: Community and individual level dominance analysis
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Zihan", "Zhu", email = "zxz1586@case.edu",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for dominance analysis of microbial communities,
    including dominance Lorenz curves, Lorenz-Wasserstein dissimilarity, 
    alpha-scale dominance (scarcity and Gini), and individual-level stable/opportunistic
    dominance summaries.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Depends: 
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    stats,
    matrixStats,
    dplyr,
    phyloseq,
    magrittr
